(2, 'Tích phân', '<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n	A.&nbsp;<span new=\"\" style=\"font-size: large; font-family: \" times=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp; KIẾN THỨC CẦN NHỚ</span></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<span new=\"\" style=\"font-size: large; font-family: \" times=\"\"><strong>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>Định nghĩa đạo h&agrave;m tại một điểm</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n	<span new=\"\" style=\"font-size: large; font-family: \" times=\"\"><strong><em>1.1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></strong><strong><em>Định nghĩa :</em></strong>&nbsp;Cho h&agrave;m số&nbsp;<img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"y=f(x)\" src=\"http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?y=f(x)\" />&nbsp;x&aacute;c định tr&ecirc;n khoảng &nbsp;(a;b) v&agrave;&nbsp;<img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"x_{0}\\in (a;b)\" src=\"http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?x_%7B0%7D%5Cin&amp;space;(a;b)\" />, đạo h&agrave;m của h&agrave;m số tại điểm&nbsp;<img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"x_{0}\" src=\"http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?x_%7B0%7D\" />&nbsp;l&agrave;&nbsp;<em>:</em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"f\'\\left ( x_{0} \\right )=\\lim_{x\\rightarrow x_{0}}\\frac{f\\left ( x \\right )-f\\left ( x_{0} \\right ) }{x-x_{0}}\" src=\"http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?f%27%5Cleft&amp;space;(&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D&amp;space;%5Cright&amp;space;)=%5Clim_%7Bx%5Crightarrow&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D%7D%5Cfrac%7Bf%5Cleft&amp;space;(&amp;space;x&amp;space;%5Cright&amp;space;)-f%5Cleft&amp;space;(&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D&amp;space;%5Cright&amp;space;)&amp;space;%7D%7Bx-x_%7B0%7D%7D\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n	<span new=\"\" style=\"font-size: large; font-family: \" times=\"\"><strong><em>1.2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></strong><strong><em>Ch&uacute; &yacute; :</em></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span new=\"\" style=\"font-size: large; font-family: \" times=\"\">Nếu k&iacute; hiệu&nbsp;<img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"\\Delta x=x-x_{0}\" src=\"http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5CDelta&amp;space;x=x-x_%7B0%7D\" />; &nbsp;<img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"\\Delta y=f\\left ( x_{0}+\\Delta x\\right )-f\\left ( x_{0} \\right )\" src=\"http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5CDelta&amp;space;y=f%5Cleft&amp;space;(&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D+%5CDelta&amp;space;x%5Cright&amp;space;)-f%5Cleft&amp;space;(&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D&amp;space;%5Cright&amp;space;)\" />&nbsp;th&igrave; :</span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"f\'\\left ( x_{0} \\right )=\\lim_{x\\rightarrow x_{0}}\\frac{f\\left ( x_{0}-\\Delta x \\right )-f\\left ( x_{0} \\right ) }{x-x_{0}}=\\lim_{\\Delta x\\rightarrow 0}\\frac{\\Delta y}{\\Delta x}\" src=\"http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?f%27%5Cleft&amp;space;(&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D&amp;space;%5Cright&amp;space;)=%5Clim_%7Bx%5Crightarrow&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D%7D%5Cfrac%7Bf%5Cleft&amp;space;(&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D-%5CDelta&amp;space;x&amp;space;%5Cright&amp;space;)-f%5Cleft&amp;space;(&amp;space;x_%7B0%7D&amp;space;%5Cright&amp;space;)&amp;space;%7D%7Bx-x_%7B0%7D%7D=%5Clim_%7B%5CDelta&amp;space;x%5Crightarrow&amp;space;0%7D%5Cfrac%7B%5CDelta&amp;space;y%7D%7B%5CDelta&amp;space;x%7D\" /><br />\r\n		<span new=\"\" style=\"font-size: large; font-family: \" times=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;.</span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span new=\"\" style=\"font-size: large; font-family: \" times=\"\">Nếu h&agrave;m số c&oacute; đạo h&agrave;m tại&nbsp;<img align=\"absmiddle\" alt=\"x_{0}\" src=\"http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?x_%7B0%7D\" />&nbsp;th&igrave; n&oacute; li&ecirc;n tục tại điểm đ&oacute;.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Xem th&ecirc;m tại:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://toanhoc247.com/ly-thuyet-bai-tap-dao-ham-chi-tiet-day-du-a5149.html#ixzz4oS24Lf3b\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 153); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;\">http://toanhoc247.com/ly-thuyet-bai-tap-dao-ham-chi-tiet-day-du-a5149.html#ixzz4oS24Lf3b</a></span></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n	1. a) Cho f(x) = (x + 10)<sup>6&nbsp;</sup>. T&iacute;nh f&quot;(2).</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; b) Cho f(x) = sin 3x. T&iacute;nh f&quot;<span 1998=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"mjx-math\" data-mathml=\"&lt;math xmlns=\" http:=\"\" id=\"MJXc-Node-1\" math=\"\" role=\"presentation\" span=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0px;\" tabindex=\"0\" www.w3.org=\"\"><span class=\"mjx-mrow\" id=\"MJXc-Node-2\" style=\"display: inline-block; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><span class=\"mjx-mrow\" id=\"MJXc-Node-3\" style=\"display: inline-block; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><span class=\"mjx-mo\" id=\"MJXc-Node-4\" style=\"display: inline-block; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R\" style=\"display: block; white-space: pre; font-family: MJXc-TeX-size1